Prometo.

375
00:21:57,980 --> 00:21:59,399
Riley!

376
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:01,370
Harper.

377
00:22:04,956 --> 00:22:08,036
Desculpe...
Riley, esta é a Abby.

378
00:22:08,037 --> 00:22:09,949
- Abby é minha...
- Órfã.

379
00:22:09,950 --> 00:22:11,516
